    <item>
      <title>Haidar 的对冲基金在客户经历过山车般的波动中飙升 16%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/haidar-s-hedge-fund-soars-16-in-respite-from-worst-ever-losses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宏观交易员赛义德·海达尔 (Said Haidar) 带领他的对冲基金取得了 19 个月以来的最大收益，让客户暂时摆脱了自 20 多年前推出该策略以来最糟糕的表现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/haidar-s-hedge-fund-soars-16-in-respite-from-worst-ever-losses</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 14:30:15 GMT</pubDate>
